# Forked from https://github.com/android-rpi/local_manifests

# Download Android source with local_manifests
 Refer to http://source.android.com/source/downloading.html

 $ repo init -u https://android.googlesource.com/platform/manifest -b android-11.0.0_r37
 $ git clone https://github.com/mlorenzati/local_manifests .repo/local_manifests -b arpi-11
 $ repo sync

# Build for Raspberry Pi 4
 https://github.com/mlorenzati/device_arpi_rpi4/tree/arpi-11

Use -j[n] option on sync & build steps, if build host has a good number of CPU cores.